release_note: We re excited to announce a fresh update for Voice Recorder now fully compatible with iOS 17! Our team has been hard at work making sure that your experience is smoother and more reliable. Here s what you can expect in the latest version: iOS 17 Compatibility: We ve fine tuned Voice Recorder to ensure seamless performance on the latest iOS version. Enjoy all the new features and enhancements of iOS 17 without any hiccups. Bug Fixes: We ve ironed out those pesky bugs that might have been interrupting your recording experience. Your sessions should now be more stable than ever. Performance Improvements: We ve made under the hood improvements to make the app faster and more responsive. Record playback and edit without any lag. Thank you for choosing Voice Recorder for your audio recording needs. We re constantly striving to make our app better and your feedback plays a crucial part in that process. If you ve enjoyed using the app consider leaving us a review in the App Store. It helps us a lot and we really appreciate it. Stay tuned for more updates and happy recording!
